tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE design_files (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    file_name STRING,
    file_type STRING,
    file_content BYTES,
    access_level ENUM('restricted', 'confidential', 'classified')
);

CREATE TABLE sensitive_design_files (
    file_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    file_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    creator VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
    creation_date DATE NOT NULL,
    permission_level VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE intellectual_property (
    ip_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    ip_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    ip_owner VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
    ip_type VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    ip_classification VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE access_control (
    access_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    file_id INT NOT NULL,
    user_id INT NOT NULL,
    access_level VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    grant_date DATE NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE design_files (
  file_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  file_name VARCHAR(255),
  file_type VARCHAR(50),
  file_size INT,
  access_level VARCHAR(20)
)

CREATE TABLE users (
  user_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  username VARCHAR(50),
  password VARCHAR(50),
  email VARCHAR(100),
  role VARCHAR(20)
)

CREATE TABLE permissions (
  permission_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  permission_name VARCHAR(50),
  description TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE user_permissions (
  user_id INT,
  permission_id INT,
  FOREIGN KEY (user_id) REFERENCES users(user_id),
  FOREIGN KEY (permission_id) REFERENCES permissions(permission_id)
)

CREATE TABLE design_files (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    file_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    file_type VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    owner_id INT NOT NULL,
    created_at TIMESTAMP NOT NULL
)

CREATE TABLE users (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    name VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
    email VARCHAR(255) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
    role VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL
)

CREATE TABLE access_logs (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT NOT NULL,
    file_id INT NOT NULL,
    access_time TIMESTAMP NOT NULL
)

CREATE TABLE roles (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    role_name VARCHAR(50) UNIQUE NOT NULL
)

CREATE TABLE permissions (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    role_id INT NOT NULL,
    permission_type VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL
)
